    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the whole company, the funding, all of it. i'm looking at the debt numbers and i just... i can't even think about going home. i can't look my wife in the eye and tell her i lost everything we built. the shame is just too much. i feel like there's no way out of this.",
