      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I can see why you'd think that, but it's not a solution. It's a temporary escape, but it would only make things worse in the long run. You'd be avoiding the pain, but you'd also be denying your family the opportunity to heal and move on. And think about the emotional toll on your wife - she's already feeling the weight of your failure, and if you just disappear, she'll be left to pick up the pieces alone.",
